snippet.title: Transylvania
snippet.description: Transylvania Point 'n click story in which your task is to help Mr. Potato with escaping from scary Transylvania.

snippet.title: Vanguards
snippet.description: Vanguards Action puzzle. Use the super powers of all superheroes to clear out the bad guys in each stage.

snippet.title: Super Fishing
snippet.description: Super Fishing Fishing game. Try to catch as many fish as you can. Complete the challenges to earn more cash.

snippet.title: Van TT
snippet.description: Van TT Race your van around the track. Pickup the yellow cones to score bonuses.

snippet.title: Ninja Ball
snippet.description: Ninja Ball Swing on your rope and collect the stars before you run out of time to advance to the next level.

snippet.title: Gemclix Blitz
snippet.description: Gemclix Blitz Fast paced match 3 game. Survive as long as you can removing the blocks for the highest score.

snippet.title: Skywire 2
snippet.description: Skywire 2 Action game. Get the people in the roller coaster safe to the end of each track dodging dangers.

snippet.title: Jewel Thief
snippet.description: Jewel Thief Steal the jewels and try to exit the store without being caught to advance to the next level.

snippet.title: Office PaintBall
snippet.description: Office PaintBall Shoot all the smiley's. You must achieve 70% efficiency to advance to the next level.

snippet.title: Van Jellies
snippet.description: Van Jellies Wiggly, wobbly, why won't you cooperate?! Stay on the beam, boy!
